west failure surface equatorial velocity is 120 km/s (0.30 Omega_c)\nfor the l = 2 p_2 mode, but failure velocities between 240 and 300 km/s\n(0.58-0.69 Omega_c)are more typical.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Mar 2008 21:13:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
